    <abstract>
      <t>Virtual Subnet is a BGP/MPLS IP VPN-based subnet extension solution which is intended for building Layer3 network virtualization overlays within and/or across data centers. This document describes a mechanism for reducing the RIB size of PE routers in the Virtual Subnet context.</t>
